1. *Ulaz* je bio zatvoren. (The entrance was closed)
2. Oni su ušli kroz *ulaz* za zaposlene. (They entered through the employees' entrance) 
3. Učenici su napustili školu kroz *ulaz* za ispis. (The students left the school through the exit)
4. On je ušao kroz *ulaz* na drugi sprat. (He entered through the entrance to the second floor)
5. Ona je ušla kroz *ulaz* u dvorište. (She entered through the entrance to the courtyard) 
6. Oni su se okupili ispred *ulaza*. (They gathered in front of the entrance)